<plot>This short follows modern-day blacksmith George Garfield as he shoes horses for various Hollywood celebrities. Among them are 'Joel McCrea' (qv), whom he visits at his ranch, and 'Guinn 'Big Boy' Williams' (qv), whose polo pony needs a new shoe. Some of the celebrities he supposedly visits are not shown together with him on the screen.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?514195</url></doc>
